    "# SmartAssist Vision Analytics - Data Analysis Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "This Jupyter Notebook provides an interactive walkthrough of the data analysis performed on the SmartAssist Vision device's operational data. The data, extracted from an HTML dashboard, covers a six-month period (December 2025 – June 2026) and offers insights into detection performance, AI confidence, and device behavior.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Table of Contents\n",
    "\n",
